textBeforeTable: See our top ranked players in the European region here. Pull up a chair and join us in recognizing the current top ranked Hearthstone players in the Americas region! This data is up-to-date as of yesterday, March 24th, 2014. Please note that this list only includes players who are currently at Legend rank. If not enough players are at Legend rank to display here, this list will display the top ranked Legend players as well as other top Ranked Play players in order of stars accumulated. This information is currently not immediately visible in-game and we are offering it as a nod of appreciation to those who continue to test, participate, and compete in our new Ranked Play mode. Here are the current rankings from Test Season 4 of the Americas region. Many of you have been participating in Ranked Play mode, but these players have gone the extra mile and worked their way up the current ladder system to become one of the top ranked Hearthstone players! #1 - 2014/03/26 05:00:00 PM Share on Facebook Share on Twitter Forum Quote: HTML URL: Forum URL:
